product_name: Grande CosmeticsGrandeWRAP Tubing Mascara with ProVitamin B5
summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty FreeGrande Cosmetics' high-tech GrandeWRAP Tubing Mascara with ProVitamin B5 is designed to wrap lashes in length and nourishment for an instantly extended effect and conditioned, healthier looking lashes over time.
details: DetailsFeaturesTubing mascara for length, all-day wear & easy removalInfused with conditioning ProVitamin B5 & mango butterTapered brush wraps each lash in 360 degree tubesDome-shaped tip builds volume & helps fan out inner and outer cornersStays in place all day, no transfer or smudging on skinKey IngredientsProVitamin B5 conditions lashesMango butter moisturizes & helps soften lashesVegan beeswax locks lashes in placeResearch Results91% felt it locked in place without flaking**In a consumer study.Item 2636233How To UsePosition the brush at the base of your lashes & sweep upwards, wiggling brush from side-to-side as you coat.Add additional layers until desired length, lift & separation is achieved.Pro Tip: Use the dome-shaped bristles at the tip to precisely coat each individual lash and add extra volume.Mess-free removal with just warm water!Using a cotton pad or your fingers, wet lashes warm water. This will help soften the mascara for easy removal.Gently glide downwards until tubes slide off lashes.IngredientsWater/Aqua/Eau, Polyurethane-35, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax/Cera Carnauba/Cire De Carnauba, Synthetic Beeswax, Glyceryl Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Butylene Glycol, Stearic Acid, Palmitic Acid, Aminomethyl Propanol, Phenoxyethanol, Acacia Senegal Gum, Mangifera Indica (Mango) Seed Butter, Methylpropanediol, Panthenol, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Tocopherol, Iron Oxides (CI 77499).Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details

reviews.headline: Completely "fine" Mascara
reviews.comments: If  you are looking for a mascara that shows your lashes exactly as they are, this product is for you. It makes your lashes darker but does not enhance them, add volume or provide additional length. There is nothing wrong with it, just not the product for me.

reviews.headline: Great formula!
reviews.comments: This is a great tubing mascara! The formula is not too thick or wet, and it wears beautifully. I wore it through hot desert hikes with no flaking! I'm only detracting a star because I don't like a spiky synthetic wand. If that's your preference, you'll love this!

reviews.headline: Love this for natural enhancement!
reviews.comments: Absolutely love this mascara! It gives that 'I woke up like this look'. I have naturally long and curly lashes. Dark roots and blonde tips, so they don't look full without added color. This mascara adds just enough to accentuate my natural lashes. It doesn't smear and somehow comes off so easily when I wash my makeup off it is truly a mascara dream. For my girlies who like more dramatic look I wouldn't recommend this one, but for my naturals this should be your go to.

reviews.headline: I would not buy again
reviews.comments: This irritated my eyes and made them swollen. It made it hard to blink and is the only mascara that has done this.

reviews.headline: I finally found it!
reviews.comments: The best tubing mascara ever! I have tried so many different brands and they all flake, except this one!

reviews.headline: I WOULD BUY AGAIN
reviews.comments: GOES ON GOOD STAY LOVE

reviews.headline: Nope..
reviews.comments: I hate this mascara.. it doesn't add length or volume, it made my lashes stick together, and the bristles on the wand are too long and pokey...

reviews.headline: Good tubing mascara
reviews.comments: I think tbat considering that it is both a tubing madcara and a lash conditioner/ contains lengthening ingredients it is well worth the price. It layers well and is easy to remove. I have not experienced flaking and it lated well with my lash primer from este.

reviews.headline: No..
reviews.comments: I hate this mascara. It's too thin and the wand bristles are too long. It adds color to may lashes but that's it, no volume and no length.

reviews.headline: No
reviews.comments: This mascara was not for me. It seems like there was hardly anything in the tube, so therefore nothing went on my lashes.

reviews.headline: The best mascara!
reviews.comments: I wrote a review of this product saying it wasnt worth 20 dollars but after a few weeks of using it I am impressed and will repurchase. It doesn't rub off on my hair, is easy to remove with just warm water and gives me bold lashes.

reviews.headline: Mixed emotions…
reviews.comments: I have mixed emotions about this mascara. I absolutely love tubing mascaras. So much so that its the only kind of mascara I use anymore. I was excited to try this one because I like to compare all the tubing masacaras on the market and GrandeWrap has me so confused. I like the wand and how precise you can get in the inner corner and the bristles give good separation at first. The formula of the mascara however is extremely wet. In order to see length I have to let each coat *almost* dry before applying another one which isn't ideal for someone who is always in a rush. Once I get to about my fifth coat (which in my opion is way too many to be able to achieve the look im going for) the lashes start to clump together because of the excessive product. I was really hoping for more out of this product and will be sticking to my Tartelette XL tubing mascara.

reviews.headline: Not worth the price
reviews.comments: Was really looking forward to trying this mascara but I get better looking lashes using maybelline.

reviews.headline: Great product
reviews.comments: The very best of all of the Grande MD mascaras.  The brush is exceptional!

reviews.headline: The worst mascara I've ever tried.
reviews.comments: Do not waste a cent on this mascara. It is AWFUL. Literally looks like nothing. The wand with the extra stuff on the top is horrible. It just gets all over your inner corner. I put it on before work and decided to take it off and go bare then use this at all.

reviews.headline: This is my new go to tubing mascara
reviews.comments: New holy grail mascara unlocked! GrandeWRAP gives me the cleanest, longest lashes without any smudging or flaking even through full days and workouts. It builds beautifully, comes off like a dream with just water, and actually feels good for my lashes with the ProVitamin B5. I'm genuinely obsessed and I'm so thankful I got to try this complimentary from grandecosmetics because i will actually repurchase this time and time again. This is the best tubing mascara I've tried, and I've tried quite a few at this point!

reviews.headline: Great mascara!!
reviews.comments:
I received this complimentary from GrandeCosmetics WRAP Tubing Mascara with ProVitamin B5, and here's my honest opinion:

I really liked this mascara. It gave my lashes beautiful length and definition without clumping. The tubing formula is super lightweight and stays in place all day without smudging or flaking. My lashes looked longer, lifted, and still felt soft thanks to the ProVitamin B5.

If you're looking for a clean, long-lash look that's easy to remove at the end of the day, this one is worth trying.

reviews.headline: Love it!
reviews.comments: Love love this mascara. Love how it makes my lashes long longer and thicker and doesn't smudge. The formula is so easy to apply and gives a beautiful look to my natural lashes. It lasts all day and you can build it up for more dramatic look. Highly recommend. Complimentary from grandecosmetics

reviews.headline: Love this
reviews.comments: Needed a new mascara and was excited to try this one out complimentary from grande cosmetics. Working great for me so far it goes on clean and makes my lashes pop without being clumpy or too heavy. Happy with this!

reviews.headline: I love this mascara!
reviews.comments: Gifted by grandecosmetics! I love this mascara! It gives me length, and separation without weighing my lashes down. It's easy to remove at the need of the day

media.headline: Great for Smudge-Free Wear, But I Hoped for More Length
I never knew I needed a tubing mascara so badly!
I would buy this for my mom

faceoff_positive.comments:
Gifted by Grande Cosmetics. I've been loving the GrandeWRAP Tubing Mascara with ProVitamin B5! Unlike traditional mascaras, this formula uses tubing technology, which means it wraps around each lash for incredible definition and length—without clumping or flaking throughout the day.

One of the biggest perks is its smudge-proof and water-resistant wear. I have oily eyelids, and most mascaras tend to smudge under my eyes, but this one stays put all day without any raccoon-eye effect. Despite its longevity, removal is a breeze—just warm water and a gentle massage, and the tubes slide right off, no harsh rubbing or makeup remover needed!

I also appreciate the ProVitamin B5 in the formula, which helps condition and strengthen my lashes over time. The wand evenly coats each lash, providing a natural yet noticeable lift and length. If you're looking for a mascara that delivers definition, durability, and easy removal, GrandeWRAP Tubing Mascara is definitely worth trying!
